(      1,000     2,000     1,000     4,000 )
(     -1,000     0,000    -1,000    -2,000 )
(      2,000    -1,000     5,000     6,000 )

Coefficients matrix:
(      1,000     2,000     1,000 )
(     -1,000     0,000    -1,000 )
(      2,000    -1,000     5,000 )

Coefficients matrix determinant:
|      1,000     2,000     1,000 |
|     -1,000     0,000    -1,000 | =      6,000
|      2,000    -1,000     5,000 |

Triangle matrix:
(      1,000     2,000     1,000     4,000 )
(      0,000     2,000     0,000     2,000 )
(      0,000     0,000     3,000     3,000 )

Solution matrix:
(      1,000 )
(      1,000 )
(      1,000 )

